Insider Activity


Individual




Mark P. Frissora



Mr. Mark P. Frissora is President & Chief Executive Officer at Caesars Entertainment Operating Co., Inc., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Caesars Entertainment Corp., Independent Director at Delphi Automotive LLP, Independent Director at Delphi Automotive Plc, Independent Director at Walgreen Co., and a Member at G100. He is on the Board of Directors at Caesars Entertainment Corp., Dollar Thrifty Automotive Group, Inc., Delphi Automotive LLP, Delphi Automotive Plc, Walgreen Co., U.S. Travel Association, and World Travel & Tourism Council.
Mr. Frissora was previously employed as Chairman & Co-Chief Executive Officer by Hertz Equipment Rental Corp., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by The Hertz Corp., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Hertz Global Holdings, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Tenneco, Inc., Vice President by Aeroquip-Vickers, Inc., a Principal by Royal Philips NV, and a Principal by General Electric Co. He also served on the board at FMC Corp., NCR Corp., Delphi Holdings LLP, and Walgreens Boots Alliance, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from The Ohio State University.



